Html : A language used to create the content of the web pages using,
tags - keywords kept inside greater than and less than symbolos called as tags. 

Structure of HTML => 
<!Doctype html>
<html>        ------> Opening tag (any keyword without /)
<head>
<title>First Web Page</title>
</head>
<body>
hello world
</body>
</html>      -------> Closing tag (any keyword with /)

HTML element - Opening and closing tags together called as HTML element.
head tag -  is for putting title or seo related content or the content for the browser (like styles cdn urls, etc.)
body tag -  is for putting the content which we want to be visible on the browser.


NOTE: if there is no title tag given than the name of the html file appear as a title in the browser.

